            <a href="cal/1dd2b6de-07b0-411b-a2a2-111ca1d6bff7/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-calendar" class="text-green-600 underline hover:no-underline">Taylor Swift's Eras Tour</a>, the possibilities are endless. 
